Usage: python VCFSamplesListCreator.py -h


#ABOUT VCF SamplesList Creator
This tool's input is a vcf file. It is creating lists with samples, that have a variation in none, one or both haploids.
WARNING! Use phased flag if the vcf file is phased, or else there will be no output
It can be used as input in some programs like SweeD or OmegaPlus.


#VERSION CHANGELOG
-0.1 - CURRENT
+ header and phased options added
+ output filenames changed


